Introduction

Summer Cake is an independent South Korean singer-songwriter. She started her career as a member of the duo Highcolor. She then debuted as a soloist under the stage name Classy. She released her debut single “I Know But” on November 9, 2020.

She also participated in two survival shows: JTBC’s MIXNINE, where she ranked 16th, and Mnet’s The Voice of Korea 2020, where she reached the final four.
